        Changelog
        ---------
        0.5.0 (2019-03-25)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Adds a DataRequired validator for HTML.
          [msom]
        
        0.4.0 (2018-08-31)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Adds support for headings.
          [msom]
        
        - Adds support for links.
          [msom]
        
        - Adds support for blockquotes.
          [msom]
        
        0.3.2 (2018-08-13)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Adds IE 11 compatibility.
          [msom]
        
