          [msom]
        
        - Uses Quill 1.3.6.
          [msom]
        
        0.2.4 (2018-02-07)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Uses Quill 1.3.5.
          [msom]
        
        - Uses quoted proptery names in the widget.
          [msom]
        
        - Requires Python 3.6.
          [href]
        
